      "content": "That \"journey within\" sounds exhausting. Honestly, it feels more like I'm just done with the transit. Like the ticket has been punched and I don't need to board another train or hike another trail. There's a certain quietness in just deciding that the trip is over and you don't need to see what's around the next bend. It feels almost... right. Like a peaceful exit.",
